{
  "texts": [
    "Collaborative interaction, which consists of communication, synchronization, and collaborative editing, is another more significant form in the Metaverse.",
    "For instance, users must communicate and synchronize the information of various users in real time when they are in the same Metaverse region.",
    "Also, collaborative editing is needed when users interact across various Metaverse zones.",
    "The employment of user interaction approaches in both physical and virtual contexts has recently been proposed.",
    "Young et al."
  ]
}